headline: Mastercard Economics Institute: What moves us? The motivations behind global travel in 2025
summary: PURCHASE, N.Y., May 12, 2025--The Mastercard Economics Institute (MEI) today released Travel Trends 2025, its annual report with unique and proprietary consumer spending insights globally. While exchange rates and geopolitical dynamics can influence consumer behavior, the report highlights that passions and purpose-driven motivations remain strong drivers shaping the travel industry.
